### Welcome to Party-Radar
What is Party-Radar?
Party-Radar is a revolution off the evening. Something like th told me a friend about this idea. 
The question is why and the answer is simple. With this app, you can locate the best party in a variable radius. The radius can switcht by the user. Also included a ratingsystem and live-chats at various levels. Other features will published step by step. Actually the project is in he development phase.
